'''瑞納爾多·亞伯特·艾摩拉二世'''（{{lang-en|Reinaldo Albert Almora Jr.}}，{{bd|1994年|4月16日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手。目前效力於辛辛那提紅人，先前曾效力於小熊和大都會。
==職業生涯==
===芝加哥小熊===
====2016年====
[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，小熊隊在第一輪第6順位選進艾摩拉。6月7日，球隊因為[[荷黑·索列爾|荷黑·索列爾]]受傷而將艾摩拉拉上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-place-of-jorge-soler-on-dl-albert-almora-promoted-20160607-story.html |title=Cubs place Jorge Soler on 15-day DL, Albert Almora Jr. promoted |first=Mark |last=Gonzales |work=Chicago Tribune |date=June 7, 2016 |accessdate=June 7, 2016 |archive-date=2019-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422021656/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-cubs-place-of-jorge-soler-on-dl-albert-almora-promoted-20160607-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在6月8日面對費城人的比賽完成大聯盟生涯首次先發出賽，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-gameday-cubs-phillies-spt-0609-20160608-story.html |title=Cubs' Albert Almora Jr. makes first start in left field, first pitch moved to 12:20 p.m. |last=Gonzales |first=Mark |website=Chicago Tribune |access-date=2016-06-08 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611111326/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-gameday-cubs-phillies-spt-0609-20160608-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>並在隔天敲出大聯盟首安。

[[2016年世界大賽|2016年世界大賽]]第七戰，艾摩拉在10局上接替[[凱爾·舒瓦伯|凱爾·舒瓦伯]]擔任代跑。[[克里斯·布萊恩|克里斯·布萊恩]]擊出全壘打牆前飛球遭到接殺，而艾摩拉大膽衝向二壘且成功站上壘包。最後艾摩拉靠著[[本·佐布里斯特|本·佐布里斯特]]的二壘安打成功跑回超前分，小熊隊也拿下了睽違108年的世界大賽冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bastian |first1=Jordan |last2=Muskat |first2=Carrie |title=Chicago Cubs win 2016 World Series |url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/ |publisher=MLB |accessdate=November 3, 2016 |archive-date=2017-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130223630/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/207938228/chicago-cubs-win-2016-world-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2017年====
這年艾摩拉出賽132場比賽，打擊率為2成98，並敲出8轟與46分打點。他也在這年將登錄名姓氏從艾摩拉二世 (Almora Jr.)改成艾摩拉 (Almora)。
====2018年====
4月22日，艾摩拉靠著三次精彩的外野防守美技幫助小熊9比7拿下勝利。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/cubs/albert-almora-jr-was-all-over-coors-field-outfield |title=Albert Almora Jr. was all over the Coors Field outfield |first=Dan |last=Santaromita |website=[[NBC_News|NBC News]] |date=April 22, 2018 |accessdate=May 29, 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530031131/https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/cubs/albert-almora-jr-was-all-over-coors-field-outfield |dead-url=no }}</ref>這年他出賽152場比賽，打擊率為2成86，並敲出5轟與41分打點。[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽]]，艾摩拉在第13局遭到洛磯投手Scott Oberg三振，成為小熊隊的最後一個出局數。最後小熊1比2敗下陣來，無緣挺進分區賽。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/2018/B10020CHN2018.htm |title=Colorado Rockies 2, Chicago Cubs 1 |website=[[Retrosheet|Retrosheet]] |date=October 2, 2018 |accessdate=May 29, 2019 |archive-date=2019-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190530025925/https://www.retrosheet.org/boxesetc/2018/B10020CHN2018.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
====2019年====
這年艾摩拉成功擠進球隊的25人名單內。<ref>{{Cite web| url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/3/26/18480063/cubs-opening-day-roster-from-a-lmora-to-z-obrist| title=Cubs' Opening Day roster from A(lmora) to Z(obrist)| date=March 27, 2019| accessdate=2020-08-20| archive-date=2019-08-13| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813180717/https://chicago.suntimes.com/2019/3/26/18480063/cubs-opening-day-roster-from-a-lmora-to-z-obrist| dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他的打擊率為2成36，並敲出生涯新高的12轟與32分打點。
====2020年====
這年艾摩拉表現進入低潮，因此他的上場時間慢慢被[[伊恩·哈普|伊恩·哈普]]壓縮。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/ian-happ-is-cubs-everyday-center-fielder |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2020-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822043025/https://www.mlb.com/news/ian-happ-is-cubs-everyday-center-fielder |dead-url=no }}</ref>後來球隊又從老虎隊交易來[[卡麥隆·梅賓|卡麥隆·梅賓]]，因此艾摩拉被下放到小聯盟。整年他的打擊率為1成67，球季結束後他並未獲得球隊續約，於是他成為自由球員。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/cubs/2020/12/2/21959451/cubs-non-tender-kyle-schwarber-albert-almora |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113012005/https://chicago.suntimes.com/cubs/2020/12/2/21959451/cubs-non-tender-kyle-schwarber-albert-almora |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===紐約大都會===
2021年2月10日，他與大都會隊簽下1年合約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/30876607/albert-almora-mets-finalize-1-year-125m-contract |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-02-12 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211041001/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/30876607/albert-almora-mets-finalize-1-year-125m-contract |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他在大都會的打擊率僅1成15，沒敲出全壘打也沒有任何打點。因此最後他在10月7日遭到指定讓渡，最後成為自由球員。
==個人生活==
艾摩拉的父親老艾摩拉以前曾於古巴叛逃至美國。<ref name=trib>{{cite web |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-10-12/sports/ct-spt-1013-afl-cubs-chicago-20131013_1_albert-almora-arizona-fall-league-family-affair |title=Albert Almora: Albert Almora's dedication a family affair – Chicago Tribune |publisher=Articles.chicagotribune.com |date=October 12, 2013 |accessdate=November 14, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028155905/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-10-12/sports/ct-spt-1013-afl-cubs-chicago-20131013_1_albert-almora-arizona-fall-league-family-affair |dead-url=no }}</ref>而老艾摩拉在他兒子三歲時就開始教他打棒球。艾摩拉和另一名大聯盟好手[[曼尼·馬查多|曼尼·馬查多]]交情甚好，兩人小時候曾表示想一起拿下世界大賽冠軍。<ref name=prep>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120524&content_id=32161804&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |title=Prep star Albert Almora could be a top-10 Draft pick | MLB.com: News |publisher=Mlb.mlb.com |date= |accessdate=November 14, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015153350/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120524&content_id=32161804&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=trib/>

2016年7月21日，艾摩拉與費城76人隊的前啦啦隊員Krystal Gregorio結婚。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/chicagoinc/ct-albert-almora-wedding-chicago-inc-spt-0724-20160722-story.html |title=Cubs' Albert Almora Jr. gets married on his off-day, then sent to Iowa |work=Chicago Tribune |accessdate=December 21, 2017 |archive-date=2019-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421042356/https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/chicagoinc/ct-albert-almora-wedding-chicago-inc-spt-0724-20160722-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>他們在該年8月份迎來了第一個孩子。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-albert-krystal-almora-medical-leave-20180716-story.html |title=Cubs' Albert Almora Jr. says wife Krystal 'is doing much better' |first=Chicago Tribune |last=staff |publisher= |accessdate=2020-08-20 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003065259/http://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/baseball/cubs/ct-spt-cubs-albert-krystal-almora-medical-leave-20180716-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年與2018年的球員綽號週，艾摩拉選擇Tico作為他的綽號。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/mlb-players-weekend-to-showcase-unique-nicknames-colorful-uniforms/ |title=MLB Players Weekend to showcase unique nicknames, colorful uniforms |publisher= |date=August 10, 2017 |accessdate=2020-08-20 |archive-date=2017-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170913004031/http://chicago.suntimes.com/sports/mlb-players-weekend-to-showcase-unique-nicknames-colorful-uniforms/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>原因是因為他小時候非常調皮，因此家人給了他這個綽號。
